text: Joya Maria Azzi (; born 23 September 2000) is a Lebanese professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder or left-back for Lebanese club EFP and the Lebanon national team. ==References== ==External links== * Joya Maria Azzi at Global Sports Archive * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:People from Keserwan District Category:Lebanese women's footballers Category:Lebanon women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Women's association football fullbacks Category:Lebanese Women's Football League players Category:Lebanon women's youth international footballers Category:Zouk Mosbeh SC footballers Category:Eleven Football Pro WFC players
